These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog, pony
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the owner of the dog##8
3. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Pet   | pony | dog | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, ritmeester, montecristo
1. the montecristo-smoker is not to the left of the dannemann-smoker##8
2. the montecristo-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Cigar   | dannemann | montecristo | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
3 different games are played: go, mah-jongg, poker
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing go##1
2. the person playing go is not to the right of the person playing poker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Game   | mah-jongg | go | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, bike, tram
1. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |      3      |
| Transport   | tram | bike | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-5::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower, daisy
1. the person who growsbellflower is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsbellflower is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3     |
| Flower   | lily | bellflower | daisy |

